        "up_votes": 4,
        "down_votes": 0
      },
      "duration": 7.52
    },
    {
      "id": "39597091",
      "text": "Daar is kritiek dat Somali's geteister word wanneer hulle sake by die polisiestasie aanmeld.",
      "audio": "af/unknown/af_u_39597091.mp3",
      "tags": {
        "source_item_id": "39597091",
        "gender": "u",
        "up_votes": 2,
        "down_votes": 0
      },
      "duration": 8.1
    },
    {
      "id": "39809234",
      "text": "Maak die leerders deurgaans van die gebruik van hoofletters, spasiëring en leestekens bewus.",
      "audio": "af/unknown/af_u_39809234_capetonian.mp3",
      "tags": {
        "source_item_id": "39809234",
        "gender": "u",
        "accent": "Capetonian",
        "up_votes": 4,
        "down_votes": 0
      },
      "duration": 7.63
    },
    {
      "id": "39597093",
      "text": "Die Program van Assessering vir Besigheidstudies bestaan uit sewe take wat intern geassesseer word.",
      "audio": "af/unknown/af_u_39597093.mp3",
      "tags": {
        "source_item_id": "39597093",
        "gender": "u",
        "up_votes": 2,
        "down_votes": 0
      },
      "duration": 7.52
    },
    {
      "id": "39809235",
      "text": "Beskryf die tipe gesteente en onderliggende struktuur wat met dreineerpatroon C geassosieer word.",
      "audio": "af/unknown/af_u_39809235_capetonian.mp3",
      "tags": {
        "source_item_id": "39809235",
        "gender": "u",
        "accent": "Capetonian",
        "up_votes": 4,
        "down_votes": 0
      },
      "duration": 9.68
    },
    {
      "id": "39597119",
      "text": "Daar is verskillende maniere om 'n argument- en 'n teenargument te struktureer.",
      "audio": "af/unknown/af_u_39597119.mp3",
      "tags": {
        "source_item_id": "39597119",
        "gender": "u",
        "up_votes": 2,
        "down_votes": 0
      },
      "duration": 6.23
    },
    {
      "id": "39812027",
      "text": "Ons het die groot skoffel gebruik om die hardnekkige onkruid uit te grawe.",
      "audio": "af/unknown/af_u_39812027_capetonian.mp3",
      "tags": {
        "source_item_id": "39812027",
        "gender": "u",
        "accent": "Capetonian",
        "up_votes": 4,
        "down_votes": 0
      },
      "duration": 5.18
    },
    {
      "id": "39597210",
      "text": "Die verkoopsyfers van twee motorvervaardigers in Suid-Afrika vir 'n sesmaande-tydperk is vrygestel.",
      "audio": "af/unknown/af_u_39597210.mp3",
      "tags": {
        "source_item_id": "39597210",
        "gender": "u",
        "up_votes": 2,
        "down_votes": 0
      },
      "duration": 7.34
    },
    {
      "id": "39809371",
      "text": "Getal subsidies wat na naskoolse sorgfasiliteite oorgedra is om dienste aan kinders te verskaf.",
      "audio": "af/unknown/af_u_39809371_capetonian.mp3",
      "tags": {
        "source_item_id": "39809371",
        "gender": "u",
        "accent": "Capetonian",
        "up_votes": 4,
        "down_votes": 0
      },
      "duration": 8.75
    },
    {
      "id": "39597176",
      "text": "Die regering beskou ook marikultuur as belangrik omdat die mariene bronne aangevul moet word.",
      "audio": "af/unknown/af_u_39597176.mp3",
      "tags": {
        "source_item_id": "39597176",
        "gender": "u",
        "up_votes": 2,
        "down_votes": 0
      },
      "duration": 8.39
    },
    {
      "id": "39597042",
      "text": "Vertraging in die aanstelling van diensverskaffers maak dit moeilik om projekte betyds te voltooi.",
      "audio": "af/unknown/af_u_39597042.mp3",
      "tags": {
        "source_item_id": "39597042",
        "gender": "u",
        "up_votes": 2,
        "down_votes": 0
      },
      "duration": 7.6
    },
    {
      "id": "39597146",
      "text": "Sy het gesteun toe sy die swaar pot oplig.",
      "audio": "af/unknown/af_u_39597146.mp3",
      "tags": {
        "source_item_id": "39597146",
        "gender": "u",
        "up_votes": 2,
        "down_votes": 0
      },
      "duration": 3.71
    },
    {
      "id": "39812025",
      "text": "Die kamer is leeg - daar is niemand daar nie.",
      "audio": "af/unknown/af_u_39812025_capetonian.mp3",
      "tags": {
        "source_item_id": "39812025",
